definition: certificate/proof/to prove/to demonstrate/to confirm/variant of 症[zheng4]

sentences.english: As soon as you prove to be good, you will get more followers.
sentences.chinese: 如果事實證明你還不錯，必定會有更多追隨者。

sentences.english: The results provide empirical foundation for model-building and simulations.
sentences.chinese: 結論爲進一步建模仿真提供了實證基礎。

sentences.english: Analytic demonstration of the core competence of non-state-run listed enterprises.
sentences.chinese: 民營上市企業核心競爭力的實證分析。

sentences.english: Facts have proven that the establishment of diplomatic ties between China and Dominica conforms to the fundamental interest of both countries.
sentences.chinese: 事實證明，中多建交符合兩國的根本利益。

sentences.english: But it has proven to be wrong.
sentences.chinese: 但是，事實證明這是錯的。

sentences.english: The method of theory-model and example analysis were employed.
sentences.chinese: 採用理論建模與實證分析相結合法進行研究。

sentences.english: Chapter 3 Analysis the community workers working pressure.

sentences.english: The fact that they are so popular proves that they are useful and convenient.

sentences.english: This paper comments on the effect of corpus empirical studies on lexicology.
sentences.chinese: 論述了語料庫實證研究對詞彙學的影響和作用。

sentences.english: But one more thing, can you prove it with facts.
sentences.chinese: 但還有一點，你能用事實證明一下嗎？

sentences.english: This article presents an empirical analysis of the relationship between economic interdependence and international third-party interactions.
sentences.chinese: 本文提出經濟互賴與第三國國際互動之實證研究分析。

sentences.english: It was a probing research on the theory and practice of kinesthesis.
sentences.chinese: 本研究對動覺進行了實證與理論探討。

sentences.english: Then, penman analyze the actuality of Chinese government scale by demonstration.

sentences.english: The course is especially suited for students undertaking empirical exercise in writing their M. A. thesis.
sentences.chinese: 本課程對於寫實證研究的碩士論文特別有益。

sentences.english: However, there are few empirical researches related to middle-level managers' turnover intention.
sentences.chinese: 然而，有關中層管理者離職傾向的實證研究並不多見。

sentences.english: At the end of the paper, it takes Jianfengling National Forest Park as a case.
sentences.chinese: 最後，以尖峯嶺國家森林公園爲例作了實證研究。
